original_title: Trophy Fishing in the Canadian Yukon
overview: Fishing the “Land of the Midnight Sun” along the 38th parallel of Canada’s Northwest Territories, from the remote and beautiful Kluane Wilderness Lodge, we teamed up with owner/operator Brian Dack for some of the best Northern Pike and Giant Lake Trout fishing to be found anywhere on the planet. Only accessible by float planes, Kluane is a freshwater fisherman’s dream come true.
title: Trophy Fishing in the Canadian Yukon
